            "title": "A Phase 1, Open-label, Dose Escalation Study To Evaluate Safety, Pharmacokinetics And Pharmacodynamics Of Combined Oral C-met/Alk Inhibitor (Pf-02341066) And Pan-her Inhibitor (Pf-00299804) In Patients With Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer",
